    "patch_code": "public <T> void resetMock(T mock) {\n    MockHandlerInterface<T> oldMockHandler = getMockHandler(mock);\n    MockHandler<T> newMockHandler = new MockHandler<T>(null);\n    MockitoInternalSettings settings = Mockito.settings();\n    newMockHandler.setDefaultAnswer((settings.getDefaultAnswer()));\n    for(MethodCallRealProxy call : oldMockHandler.getRecordedInvocations()){\n        newMockHandler.addSeenMethod(call.getMethod());\n    }\n    \n    MethodInterceptorFilter newFilter = new MethodInterceptorFilter(newMockHandler,(MockSettingsImpl) settings);\n    ((Factory) mock).setCallback(0, newFilter);\n}",
